data.description: Huge master bedroom 16ft x 20ft with private suite with a 3 person corner tub and separate shower.  Also 4 build in Klipshc speakers in master bedroom and 2 in the bathroom.  Everything is wired for tv and high speed internet for every wall in the bedrooms with CAT 6A and RG6.   The living room has open concept living with 5 Klipsch speakers in wall speakers.  Stainless steel GE Profile appliances with gas stove with center grill.  Is a Vivint Smart home with cameras.  Backs up to the Ranches Golf course's driving range so no back neighbors with great mountain views.
data.whatILove: Every room is wired with cat 6A ethernet and built in 5 speakers in living and 6 in the master suite.  Fenced with a double 6ft gates for a total of 12 ft on the side of the house.  Could easily poor an RV pad beside the house and have a 12ft x 50ft with room left over.
